highlights.text: “Moonlit Floor (Kiss Me)” by LISA is the highest new entry on Top Songs Denmark at #169.
“Reposado” by Benny Jamz and Gilli has been on Top Songs Denmark the longest, at 409 days straight.
Gilli has the most spots on Top Songs Denmark. “Tropical (feat. Gilli)” is the highest at #4.
“Under Stjernerne På Himlen” by Rasmus Seebach is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Denmark, up 74 spots at #118.
